{
  "texts": [
    "The findings of this research could transform the diagnosis of epilepsy, offering faster and more precise methods and reducing the economic and social burden of this condition, especially in regions with limited access to neurology specialists.In machine learning mechanisms, hyperparameters are adjusted [6].",
    "A pipeline mechanism is used to modify these hyperparameters.",
    "It aims to chain together different steps in an organized manner to extract features and make adjustments to a model.",
    "Following this, a grid search is employed.",
    "This technique explores the best values and evaluates the model's performance for each combination of values [7].In recent years, new deep-learning mechanisms have improved the model's capacity."
  ]
}